    <p class="gd-toc__t">On this page</p>
    <a href="#s1">The basics</a>
    <a href="#s2">Snow and terrain</a>
    <a href="#s3">The helicopter and the day</a>
    <a href="#s4">Safety and avalanche</a>
    <a href="#s5">Kit and equipment</a>
